Package: mail-agent
Version: 1.0.0
Section: mail
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Pre-Depends: curl, ca-certificates
Depends: postfix, lsb-release, gnupg, software-properties-common
Recommends: dovecot-imapd
Suggests: ollama
Maintainer: Viktor Zambo <mail-agent@zamboviktor.hu>
Homepage: https://github.com/vzambo64/mail-agent
Description: AI-powered automatic email reply agent for Postfix
 Mail-Agent intercepts incoming emails and generates intelligent
 automatic replies using configurable LLM providers (OpenAI,
 Anthropic, Google Gemini, or local Ollama models).
 .
 Compatible with Ubuntu 18.04 (Bionic) and later versions.
 All dependencies are managed automatically during installation.
 .
 Features:
  - Multiple LLM provider support (OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, Ollama)
  - Sender-based rule matching with regex patterns
  - Send immediately or save to IMAP Drafts for review
  - Custom system prompts per rule
  - Comprehensive logging and error handling
